additional_data.description: The spirit of one of Japan's three legendary tanukis. He's the boss of the bake-tanukis. Everyone in their community is a master of various supernatural powers, especially those involving stealth and covert activities. They boast that stealing state secrets is like taking candy from a baby. However, they never use their powers for selfish gain, dedicating them instead to serving the greater good. This is thanks to the leadership of none other than Gyobu himself.
